    <shortlink>ux videoplayer pause method</shortlink>
    <topic parent="Video Player" parentType="object" elementName="pause Method">Video Player pause Method</topic>
    <description>
        <p>Pauses video playback for a VideoPlayer or VideoRecorderPlayer UX control.</p>
    </description>
    <prototypes>
        <prototype>videoObj.pause()</prototype>
    </prototypes>
    <discussion>
        <p>The *[js:pause()]* method pauses video playback for a [VideoPlayer] or [VideoRecorderPlayer] control.</p>
    </discussion>
    <example code="js"><![CDATA[var vObj = {dialog.object}.getControl('MYVIDEOPLAYER');
if (vObj) {
    vObj.pause();
}]]></example>
